Game written in C as my university project. My implementation of game engine (gamma.c) involved 
implementing structures like stack (implemented as dynammic array) or find union (although it is not implemented explictly in the project), and algorithms like DFS.
Game can be played in two modes - interactive mode and by command line interface.
Writing command line (batch) mode of the game required writing a parser in C, and
implementing interactive mode of the game was an opportunity to learn about ANSI escape codes.
The whole project has a docummentation in polish, which I wrote using Doxygen.
Full project description can be found: <link>
